|caption                  = President [[Richard Nixon]] waves at a 1969 Inaugural Parade float recreating his visit to [[Deshler, Ohio]].
|date                     = October 1968 <U+2013> January 1969
|time                     = 
|place                    = [[Deshler, Ohio]] <U+2013> Washington D.C.
